race.description: Wattys Rural & Domestic Fencing Mobile Pace
race.comment: SHE WHO DARES (3) was in the money two starts ago then scored a comfortable win last start over 1770m at this track, getting home by 12 metres after taking control early in proceedings. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Primary contender in a similar assignment. MEGS MONARO (1) is in good form at present. Finished fifth at his latest appearance over 1770m at this track, beaten 8 metres. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Big chance based on recent form. OAK RIDGE (4) is worth plenty of thought off a last-start win by 1.5 metres at this track over 1770m. Each way. PENCIL ME IN (9) is heading the right way, improving last time out to finish second at this track over 1770m. Include in all combinations.
